trans-unit.source: Represents a design-time editor sheet for the properties of a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression in the UI of a designer host at design time.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et ark utformingen redigeringsprogrammet for egenskaper av et <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> uttrykk i Brukergrensesnittet for designer vert under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor> class together with the RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet class to select the individual properties of a `RouteUrl` expression, and to combine the selected expression property values into a `RouteUrl` expression.
trans-unit.target: Den visuelle utformeren bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor>klassen sammen med RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet klassen for å velge individuelle egenskaper for en `RouteUrl` uttrykk, og for å samle egenskapsverdiene for uttrykket som er valgt i en `RouteUrl` uttrykk.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method returns a RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden returnerer et RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet-objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In the expressions dialog box, when you select a control property and bind it to a `RouteUrl` expression, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: I uttrykksdialogboksen når du velger egenskap for en kontroll og binde den til en `RouteUrl` uttrykk, visuelle designer kall av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the returned RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet object to prompt for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Den visuelle utformeren bruker returnerte RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet-objektet til å be om den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: Once the properties are selected, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A> method to combine the properties into a `RouteUrl` expression string.
trans-unit.target: Når egenskapene er valgt, den visuelle utformeren kaller den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>metode for å kombinere egenskapene til en `RouteUrl` uttrykket.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> property must be specified if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property is not specified.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>må være angitt hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>egenskapen er ikke angitt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property must be specified if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> is not specified.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>må være angitt hvis det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>er ikke angitt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Both properties may be specified.
trans-unit.target: Begge egenskapene kan angis.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The initial <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property values are set using the input `expression` string.
trans-unit.target: Første <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>egenskapsverdier angis ved hjelp av inndataene `expression` streng.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A> property is set using the input `serviceProvider` implementation.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>egenskapen angis ved hjelp av inndataene `serviceProvider` implementering.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression, used to initialize the expression editor sheet.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> brukes til å initialisere uttrykket redigeringsprogrammet arket uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: A service provider implementation supplied by the designer host, used to obtain additional design-time services.
trans-unit.target: En tjenesten leverandøren implementering angitt av designer verten, brukes til å hente utformingen tilleggstjenester.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression that is formed by the expression editor sheet property values.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> uttrykk som er utformet av egenskapsverdiene for uttrykket redigeringsprogrammet arket.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string for the current settings in the sheet.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> uttrykk-strengen for gjeldende innstillingene i arket.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string is valid.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> uttrykket er ugyldig.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string is valid; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> uttrykket er ugyldig; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
